features: 100% ORGANIC TAMPONS – Even though they function like an ordinary tampon, these organic tampons are made from 100% organic cotton which contains NO chlorine, dioxins, dyes, fragrances, rayon, viscose, or chemicals.

IDEAL FOR SENSITIVITY ISSUES – These all natural tampons are made with good absorbency, but also naturally hypoallergenic. These organic tampons help prevent discomfort or irritation in the sensitive, intimate parts of your body. Designed for a comfortable fit and to prevent leaks, you won’t even know you are using this tampons.

BPA FREE PLASTIC APPLICATOR – Another benefit of these organic tampons with applicator is that they come with an easy to use BPA free plastic applicator. It has Pull and Lock technology allowing it to be small enough to fit into any purse or bag but extends for easy insertion.

INDIVIDUALLY WRAPPED TRAVEL SIZE – Each organic cotton tampon is individually wrapped in biodegradable cellulose paper for safety. They are compact until you are ready to use, then just unlock and extend before insertion. This makes these organic tampons ultra-portable, perfect for women on-the-go.
Leaves more room in your purse or pocket when you carry them.
An smooth rounded tip provides an easy and comfortable insertion.
body.description: Healthy Essentials for your body and our environment. Maxim Hygiene offers healthy, sustainable hygiene products that are safe for your body and the environment. What looks like Cotton in other products is not always 100% Cotton. Wood Pulp, Ryan and Synthetic Materials that may be bleached with Chlorine are often used as a substitute in conventional women’s hygiene products. All Maxim products are made with 100% Organic and Natural Chlorine-Free Cotton to help reduce the risk of irritation, minimize the body's exposure to chemicals and feel softer.
